---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="MyDinero Privacy Policy. Learn how we protect your data and respect your privacy. No data collection, no tracking, no bank connections."
>
  <div class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <article class="legal-content">
        <header class="legal-header">
          <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: January 15, 2025</p>
        </header>

        <section class="legal-section highlight-section">
          <h2>The Short Version</h2>
          <p class="highlight-text">
            MyDinero does not collect, store, or sell your personal data. Period.
          </p>
          <p>
            Your expense data stays on your devices and syncs through your personal iCloud account.
            We have no access to your financial information, and we never will.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>What Data We Collect</h2>
          <p><strong>None.</strong></p>
          <p>
            We don't collect any personal information. We don't require an email address,
            phone number, or any form of account creation. You download the app and start using it.
          </p>
          <p>
            Your expense entries, categories, budgets, and all other app data are stored locally
            on your device and optionally synced to your personal iCloud account — which only you control.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>iCloud Sync</h2>
          <p>
            MyDinero uses Apple's iCloud to sync your data across your devices (iPhone and iPad).
            This sync happens through your personal Apple Account and is protected by Apple's
            industry-leading privacy and security measures.
          </p>
          <p>
            We never see, access, or process your synced data. The sync happens directly between
            your devices and Apple's servers — we are not involved in that process.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>Analytics</h2>
          <p>
            We do not use any third-party analytics services. We do not track how you use the app,
            what screens you visit, or any other usage patterns.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you choose to submit a bug report or feature request through the app, that
            communication is sent directly to our support email and handled manually.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>Third Parties</h2>
          <p>
            MyDinero does not share any data with third parties because we don't have any data to share.
          </p>
          <p>
            The only "third party" involved is Apple, which provides the App Store distribution
            and iCloud sync services. Their privacy practices are governed by
            <a href="https://www.apple.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Apple's Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>Bank Connections</h2>
          <p>
            MyDinero does not connect to banks, credit cards, or any financial institutions.
            This is by design. We believe manual expense tracking gives you more control
            and awareness of your spending — and it means your financial credentials
            are never at risk.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>Data Deletion</h2>
          <p>
            Since all your data is stored locally on your device and in your personal iCloud,
            you have complete control over it:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Delete the app to remove all local data</li>
            <li>Use the in-app "Delete All Data" option in Settings</li>
            <li>Manage your iCloud storage through iOS Settings</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We cannot delete your data because we don't have it.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            MyDinero does not knowingly collect data from anyone, including children under 13.
            Since we collect no data, there is no personal information from children to protect.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this privacy policy from time to time. If we make significant changes,
            we will notify users through the app. The current version will always be available
            on this page with the "Last updated" date.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions about this privacy policy or our privacy practices,
            please contact us at:
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="mailto:privacy@mydinero.app">privacy@mydinero.app</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding-top: calc(72px + var(--space-16));
    padding-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .legal-content {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .legal-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .legal-header h1 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .legal-updated {
    color: var(--color-white-50);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
  }

  .legal-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .legal-section h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .legal-section p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .legal-section ul {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
  }

  .legal-section li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--color-white-70);
  }

  .legal-section a {
    color: var(--color-green-500);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .legal-section a:hover {
    color: var(--color-green-400);
  }

  .highlight-section {
    background-color: var(--color-gray-800);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-green-500);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: var(--space-6);
  }

  .highlight-text {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-green-500);
  }
</style>
